metadata.description: Fly deep into unknown regions of the multiverse aboard SpaceXY. Into the cradle of life.  A place where stars are born.  Penetrate the Falwell Nebula and witness firsthand The Creators majestic realm.  Life always finds a way! Isn't it interesting how patterns repeat themselves through nature?  Ready for entry captain...
metadata.name: SPACE INVADERS: COLONIZING THE FALWELL NEBULA (experience with 3-D glasses)
metadata.subtitle: Don't worry. Jerry is keeping an eye on things.
